pYsGZaakr%2FszHQdc4%2B4ddc640yZrNs%3D&h=b5d0a298\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1093609467325407&amp;id=617828444903514&amp;refsrc=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2F&amp;_rdr</a><br />\n<br />\n93年講到2019 講到口臭班藍絲都仲係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1878735aae5edcc8c7d68795a83a3ad3bcdb0424","tid":1328355,"uid":20914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:41:45.000Z","msg":"呢個世界冇話全部要要晒，點都要作出選擇<br />\n良知定糧支自己揀"},{"pid":"2104970533e3ddaa9087b243a02090be094d88cc","tid":1328355,"uid":133806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T08:03:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-48908246\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-48908246&d=bTkwEGnHH2OXdpYsGZaakr%2FszHQdc4%2B4ddc640yZrNs%3D&h=93b5099b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-48908246&h=60c2905c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-48908246</a>"},{"pid":"25a55d3a14bbd4e7ad90b00dfaf6dd8407c63736","tid":1328355,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T08:08:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/Zng1s5U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZng1s5U.jpg&h=21b38f96&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}